<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: <%= @header_color %>;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
    }
    .code-box {
      background-color: white;
      border: 2px dashed #ccc;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: <%= @header_color %>;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Your VIP Access Code</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello,</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for being a valued customer of <%= @restaurant.name %>! We're excited to provide you with VIP access to our online ordering system.</p>
      
      <p>Here is your exclusive VIP code:</p>
      
      <div class="code-box">
        <%= @vip_code.code %>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>How to use your VIP code:</strong></p>
      <ol>
        <li>Visit our online ordering page at <a href="<%= ENV['FRONTEND_URL'] %>"><%= ENV['FRONTEND_URL'] %></a></li>
        <li>Add your desired items to your cart</li>
        <li>Enter your VIP code during checkout</li>
        <li>Skip the lines and enjoy priority service!</li>
      </ol>
      
      <p>With this VIP code, you'll be able to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Skip the regular ordering lines</li>
        <li>Order food online for pickup</li>
        <li>Sit back and wait for your order to be ready for pickup</li>
        <li>Receive notifications when your order is ready</li>
        <li><strong>Note:</strong> This VIP access is for <%= @restaurant.name %> food items only</li>
      </ul>
      
      <% if @vip_code.max_uses %>
        <p><strong>Note:</strong> This code can be used <%= @vip_code.max_uses %> times.</p>
      <% end %>
      
      <p><strong>Important:</strong> Pick up must be with someone who has VIP identification (lanyard/wrist band).</p>
      
      <p>We look forward to serving you soon!</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>
      The <%= @restaurant.name %> Team</p>
      
      <a href="<%= ENV['FRONTEND_URL'] %>" class="button">Order Now</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to you because you were selected as a VIP customer.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= Date.today.year %> <%= @restaurant.name %>. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
